===Etymology===
From {{etyl|eo|en}} {{term|esperanto||one who hopes|lang=eo}}, from {{F.}} {{term|espérer|lang=fr}}, from {{L.}} {{term|sperare||to [[hope]]|lang=la}}. Originally, this was the pseudonym assumed by the language's creator, L. L. Zamenhof, and the language was called {{term|Lingvo Internacia||international language|lang=eo}}.

